{"tid":1083173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我個Friend住公屋，上條女屋企見家長 點知發生咗件咁嘅事。。。","createTime":"2019-03-29T12:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-03T10:29:50.000Z","uid":11598,"like":5914,"dislike":49,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"b9259a6418fa18926c3340c4bbb23eb317c352a3","tid":1083173,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說我朋友一直都係住公屋，咁佢上年識咗個女朋友<br />\n前幾日就上佢女朋友屋企見家長<br />\n一開始大家坐低食飯都係講啲門面嘢架喇<br />\n之後又問吓我朋友做盛行呀 搵幾錢到<br />\n然後就開始嚟料 問我朋友住邊 有冇諗住置業呀咁<br />\n我朋友都好老實咁答佢住公屋<br />\n點知伯母就開始扯火：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 伯母，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 我朋友<br />\n<br />\n伯母：「結婚呢！就要門當戶對！ 竹門對竹門，<strong>木門對木門</strong>！」<br />\n其實我朋友平時都算係幾好脾氣嗰啲人嚟，但係今次就好似撻着咗個制咁<br />\n佢下一秒就企起身 嬲爆爆咁行去門口度，伯母仲以為佢想走 講咗句「唔送喇喎！」<br />\n點知我朋友行埋度門口到，大大力起勢咁拍度門，啪啪啪！一路拍一路講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「伯母！你哋都係木門咋！！ 」<br />\n</span><br />\n伯母聽完之後呆撚咗 口都合唔埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友事後講返比我聽 笑撚到我啲腸都跌晒出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6175bafaf99b1f0a8eb3c2c15c91f291748f81","tid":1083173,"uid":212099,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65fef4379e4008d6d0e17d641e25ff0205b972a6","tid":1083173,"uid":48286,"like":1956,"dislike":5,"score":1951,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:22:06.000Z","msg":"創作力量同幻想會嚇你一跳"},{"pid":"35541c7d0060b6f