ss=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37713e9ae928fc82b0bba39f2f1ba76068fdd1b8","tid":1083173,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:19:07.000Z","msg":"同伯母講 我搭巴士返學 睇下會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad8a6f49fddcd10b520d5d5801ce10c992c2eba1","tid":1083173,"uid":1130,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"74d2d87eb01b97bdbd2ad7fa454f366b674b1404","tid":1083173,"uid":41943,"like":169,"dislike":2,"score":167,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:20:20.000Z","msg":"家家户户都木門嫁啦 你住Beverly hill你屋企門都係木門嫁<br />\n所以木門對木門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:20:53.000Z","msg":"我大你一對鐵閘"},{"pid":"cd9f816ba3995e3bb317927f2381309e0c4187cd","tid":1083173,"uid":226663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"63376888a0c59673dc9fdbd401dac087f7c8d9b9","tid":1083173,"uid":134323,"like":34,"dislike":448,"score":-414,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:23:53.000Z","msg":"我住公屋揸林保，三層樓收租<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:23:09.000Z","msg":"關我撚事"},{"pid":"0a0c2e3e046cc4498d4288e74dd93ad201293295","tid":1083173,"uid":101591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:26:16.000Z","msg":"回帶？"},{"pid":"9344aea7586f2db595734ce6bda358662d9e9be9","tid":1083173,"uid":128953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da1db612d11679b248a496427f476cc0396a140b","tid":1083173,"uid":57898,"like":10,"dislike":146,"score":-136,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T13:35:29.000Z","msg":"在民間，千百年來，門就一直作為住宅的重要組成，起著方便出入、掩護、防盜等基本功能。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在農業社會，老百姓日出而作日落而息，門就在那一進一出之間默默計數著光陰的流逝。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n封建的階級社會離不開貧富分化，門，自然也起到區分貧富的功能。 富人為了顯示身份和地位，少不免就在門上下功夫，名貴的木料、精雕細琢的紋理圖案，再加上巧妙的設計施工，目的就為了彰顯大戶人家的氣派。 而窮人的門往往不過就是簡單的木板或者樊籬。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以&ldquo;門當戶對&rdquo;的一種更為通俗的說法是&ldquo;木門對木門，竹門對竹門&rdquo;。 <span style=\"color: red;\">木門指的是富人，竹門當人就是指窮人了。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>er......</strong></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:43:29.000Z","msg":"不管木門竹門，關到就係好門。"},{"pid":"1223daa537bc9a65a32353bf50ae2f53b872b2c5","tid":1083173,"uid":171985,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b9259a6418fa18926c3340c4bbb23eb317c352a3","tid":1083173,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"是咁的，話說我朋友一直都係住公屋，咁佢上年識咗個女朋友<br />\n前幾日就上佢女朋友屋企見家長<br />\n一開始大家坐低食飯都係講啲門面嘢架喇<br />\n之後又問吓我朋友做盛行呀 搵幾錢到<br />\n然後就開始嚟料 問我朋友住邊 有冇諗住置業呀咁<br />\n我朋友都好老實咁答佢住公屋<br />\n點知伯母就開始扯火：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 伯母，<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> = 我朋友<br />\n<br />\n伯母：「結婚呢！就要門當戶對！ 竹門對竹門，<strong>木門對木門</strong>！」<br />\n其實我朋友平時都算係幾好脾氣嗰啲人嚟，但係今次就好似撻着咗個制咁<br />\n佢下一秒就企起身 嬲爆爆咁行去門口度，伯母仲以為佢想走 講咗句「唔送喇喎！」<br />\n點知我朋友行埋度門口到，大大力起勢咁拍度門，啪啪啪！一路拍一路講：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />「伯母！你哋都係木門咋！！ 」<br />\n</span><br />\n伯母聽完之後呆撚咗 口都合唔埋 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友事後講返比我聽 笑撚到我啲腸都跌晒出嚟<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"咁分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />嘅作用喺咩？"},{"pid":"e824ef833f0c1df17d44277fe2068f4d